<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>关于 MindFlow</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.10.0/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    <style>
        .hero-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f7fa 0%, #c3cfe2 100%);
            padding: 80px 0;
        }
        .feature-icon {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #0d6efd;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .tech-badge {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            padding: 8px 15px;
            margin: 5px;
            border-radius: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="d-flex flex-column min-vh-100">

    <!-- 导航栏 (保持一致) -->
    <nav class="navbar navbar-dark bg-dark">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand fw-bold" href="/">MindFlow</a>
            <a href="/" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-sm">返回创作</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- 1. Hero 区域：品牌理念 -->
    <section class="hero-section text-center">
        <div class="container">
            <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold mb-3">思维流淌的地方</h1>
            <p class="lead text-secondary mb-4" style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
                MindFlow 是一个专注于极简写作与深度交流的内容平台。<br>
                我们相信，每一个微小的想法，都值得被记录和分享。
            </p>
            <a href="https://github.com/xsxox/MindFlow" target="_blank" class="btn btn-dark btn-lg px-4 gap-3">
                <i class="bi bi-github"></i> 访问 GitHub
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 2. 核心特性：像产品介绍一样展示功能 -->
    <section class="py-5 bg-white">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row g-4 text-center">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="p-3">
                        <i class="bi bi-markdown feature-icon"></i>
                        <h4 class="fw-bold">Markdown 支持</h4>
                        <p class="text-muted">原生的 Markdown 渲染引擎，让排版回归纯粹，专注于内容创作本身。</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="p-3">
                        <i class="bi bi-chat-square-quote feature-icon"></i>
                        <h4 class="fw-bold">实时交互</h4>
                        <p class="text-muted">基于 Ajax 的无刷新评论系统，让思想的碰撞更加流畅，无需等待页面重载。</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="p-3">
                        <i class="bi bi-shield-lock feature-icon"></i>
                        <h4 class="fw-bold">权限管理</h4>
                        <p class="text-muted">完善的 RBAC 角色权限控制，保障创作者的内容安全与管理便捷。</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 3. 技术架构：把作业要求包装成技术栈 -->
    <section class="py-5 bg-light">
        <div class="container text-center">
            <h3 class="fw-bold mb-4">Under the Hood</h3>
            <p class="text-muted mb-4">MindFlow 基于现代化的 Web 技术栈构建，追求性能与开发体验的平衡。</p>
            
            <div class="d-flex justify-content-center flex-wrap" style="max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;">
                <span class="badge bg-success tech-badge">Node.js</span>
                <span class="badge bg-secondary tech-badge">Express</span>
                <span class="badge bg-danger tech-badge">MongoDB</span>
                <span class="badge bg-warning text-dark tech-badge">EJS SSR</span>
                <span class="badge bg-info text-dark tech-badge">Bootstrap 5</span>
                <span class="badge bg-primary tech-badge">MVC Architecture</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 4. 底部：极简风格 -->
    <footer class="text-center py-4 mt-auto bg-white border-top">
        <div class="container">
            <p class="mb-0 text-muted">
                Created with <i class="bi bi-heart-fill text-danger"></i> by 
                <strong>sunrise</strong>
            </p>
            <small class="text-muted">Open Source Project &copy; 2026</small>
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>